{"_path":"/maps/_ai/agents/a2ui","_dir":"agents","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"A2UI","description":"Google 推出的声明式 UI 协议，让 AI Agent 能生成富交互界面","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"a2ui-是什么"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A2UI 是什么？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Google 推出的声明式 UI 协议，让 AI Agent 能生成富交互界面。Agent 输出 JSON 描述界面结构，客户端用原生组件渲染，无需执行任意代码，兼顾安全性与原生体验。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://a2ui.org/introduction/what-is-a2ui/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"What is A2UI?"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"为什么需要-a2ui"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"为什么需要 A2UI？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"纯文本交互效率低。比如订餐厅需要多轮问答，而 A2UI 让 Agent 直接生成表单（日期选择器、时间选择器、提交按钮），用户一步完成操作。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"核心技术原理"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"核心技术原理？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"声明式 JSON"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：Agent 发送 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"surfaceUpdate"}]},{"type":"text","value":"、"},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"dataModelUpdate"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 等消息描述 UI"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"客户端渲染"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：用 Angular、Flutter、React 等原生框架渲染，继承应用样式"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"跨平台"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：同一套 JSON 可在 Web、移动端、桌面